					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Try &quot;At this point, SCP-3659's rubber components will fuse at their junctions to form the shape of a juvenile Triceratops, and eject the subject.&quot;</p> <p>or &quot;At this point, SCP-3659's rubber components will fuse at their junctions to form the shape of a juvenile Triceratops, and disgorge the subject.&quot;</p> <p>Also, +1 from me just for the phrase &quot;a visually nonanomalous triceratops&quot;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
