					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Well, now I've got an image stuck in my head that it is like that animated gif of a hypercube; the suit everting through it's own substance by way of a fifth (rubber reptilian) dimension axis that would turn our eyeballs and brains into lizard flesh were we even to attempt to <em>conceive</em> of how it moves.</p> <p>And we shall name this fifth dimension&#8230; Kaiju.</p> <p>Length, width, depth, time, and kaiju.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
