				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10361007/scp-3659#post-4161859</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 22 Feb 2019 18:06:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Faraday Cage</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1856658</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I don't understand how the rubber suit can peel off a host body after all the seams have fused. If the seams are fused&#8230; wait is this like some kind of mitosis?<br /> I'm confused because &quot;peeling&quot; implies a starting edge to peel from, and it happens right after the rubber suit becomes edgeless.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
